parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water ingress into the trunk lid can cause damage to the tail light components and wiring, leading to electrical failures, corrosion, and potentially even a fire hazard.
symptoms: Water accumulates in the trunk lid
tail light components and wiring get wet
electrical issues occur
corrosion is visible.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning driver window can cause inconvenience, distraction, and potentially even a safety hazard if the window becomes stuck in a position that obstructs the driver's view.
symptoms: The driver window rolls down on its own
the window must be rolled down completely to roll it back up
the window becomes stuck.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Space Saver Tire Changing Kit Safety Concern
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The space saver tire changing kit may not provide a safe and secure solution for changing a flat tire, potentially putting the driver or occupants at risk of harm or even homicide.
symptoms: The space saver tire changing kit is not designed for a full-size tire
the kit may not provide a secure solution for changing a flat tire
the driver or occupants may be at risk of harm.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Backup Camera and Information Screen Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the backup camera and information screen can cause a safety hazard, particularly when reversing, as the driver may not have a clear view of the surroundings.
symptoms: The backup camera fails to work
the information screen malfunctions
other functions such as the radio may also be affected
the problem recurs after attempted repairs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition system can cause the key to become stuck in the ignition, leaving the driver stranded in unsafe locations, and potentially leading to accidents or other safety risks.
symptoms: The key becomes stuck in the ignition
unable to be removed or turned.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to become stuck in gear, unable to move, or experience sudden loss of power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle will not move in drive position
the transmission pops into gear
grinding or scraping noise coming from the transmission
loss of power while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TCM can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to erratic shifting, loss of power, and other safety risks.
symptoms: The transmission shifts erratically
the vehicle radio turns on and off randomly
requiring restart while in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel pump can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, leading to a sudden loss of acceleration, which can increase the risk of an accident or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to start on the first attempt
the vehicle suddenly loses motive power
the infotainment system operates erratically
unknown warning lights are illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A fuel rail leak can cause fuel to leak from the vehicle, leading to a potential fire hazard, and may also cause the vehicle to fail to start or stall, increasing the risk of an accident or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Abnormal fuel odor
unknown fluid leaking from the vehicle
vehicle fails to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause a loss of braking ability, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal does not function
the brake pedal is soft or spongy
the vehicle is unable to stop
the airbags deploy but do not deflate afterwards.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning passenger occupancy sensor can cause false warnings, leading to driver distraction and potentially increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The warning bell chimes when there is no passenger in the seat
the warning stops when the cell phone is removed from the passenger seat
the warning stops when the seatbelt is locked.
